Title: Nature'S Walnut Foot Scrub(100 g)
Description: Your feet go ignored almost all the time, skin care routines rarely include the upkeep of the skin on your feet. You should know that the more you ignore your feet, the more problems you are going to face in the future. Women who are homemakers have so many tasks to complete on a daily basis and they neglect their own health, especially their feet. Nature's Essence Walnut Foot Scrub is formulated to suit the feet of women who overwork themselves and need a soothing foot treatment or just some pampering. Give yourself a soothing massage with this exfoliating scrub and feel the blood circulation improve simultaneously. When you improve the blood supply to your feet, you keep it protected from damage and dry skin. A soothing foot massage can relieve you from daily stress and help you relax. When this special scrub touches the skin on your feet, you get feet that are refreshed and look supple all the time. The Foot Scrub has extra-gritty particles that help in scrubbing away dry and dead skin that is too stubborn and hard to exfoliate otherwise. This Walnut Scrub is also effective in removing corns and calluses from the feet. The Scrub is infused with walnut and rose oil, the walnut particles help in exfoliating all the dead skin from your feet and also in keeping it healthy. Rose oil moisturizes and hydrates the skin and gives you smooth and silky soft feet. Directions to use Wash your feet clean with a foot soak. Apply the Foot Scrub to damp feet. Massage the scrub on the feet with circular motion for several minutes giving more attention to problem areas. Rinse off the scrub thoroughly with water and follow up with a foot massage lotion.
